[assistant] - The test uses a package-local `org.jboss.vfs.VirtualFile` test double in the same Java file so Hutool’s VFS lookup path is exercised naturally.
[assistant] - No direct reflection is used in the test.
[assistant] - I did not compile or run tests, per instruction.
